---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { ExternalLink } from 'lucide-react';
---

<Layout title="About | North Star">
    <main class="relative min-h-screen pt-32 pb-24">
        <!-- Vision -->
        <section class="container mx-auto px-6 mb-24">
            <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl italic text-white leading-relaxed text-center mb-12" style="font-family: 'Georgia Pro', Georgia, serif;">
                    To push the ecosystem forward in AI & Robotics.
                </p>
                <div class="space-y-6 text-zinc-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    <p>
                        North Star is inherently a rebellion against how things are done. We started with a hackathon - to turn talk into action and to bridge the gap between talent and companies.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        The people willing to come on a sunny Saturday and build something in exchange for pizza are the ones that will be building the future. Our culture attracts outliers and people with conviction.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        In a collaborative "Let's build it together" spirit, we gather people around ideas and problems - that can't not be solved. Whether it is simply creating environments for talent to share knowledge, hosting kids hackathons with 100 attendees and 8 venues at the same time or pushing for bringing robotics into the mainstream.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        This only exists because of the people that believed in us at the start. With a strong pay-it-forward mentality, we support the future key players of the ecosystem.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        The spark of ambition burns in everyone. You don't realize just how much potential you have. Our goal is to give you that tiny push you need to get started.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        A community is its people. We need you.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Europe's springtime is here. The ecosystem awakens. Urgency spreads.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-2xl font-medium text-white pt-4">
                        It's now or never.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Team -->
        <section class="container mx-auto px-6 mb-24">
            <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                <h2 class="text-sm font-medium text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-8 text-center">
                    Team
                </h2>
                <!-- Leadership -->
                <div class="grid grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-5 gap-6 mb-8">
                    <div class="text-center group">
                        <img src="/team/7.jpg" alt="Filip" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-2 object-cover border border-white/10 group-hover:border-white/30 transition-colors" />
                        <div class="text-white text-sm font-medium">Filip</div>
                        <div class="text-zinc-500 text-xs">CEO/CTO</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center group">
                        <img src="/team/9.jpg" alt="Oleksandr" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-2 object-cover border border-white/10 group-hover:border-white/30 transition-colors" />
                        <div class="text-white text-sm font-medium">Oleksandr</div>
                        <div class="text-zinc-500 text-xs">CPO</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center group">
                        <img src="/team/3.jpeg" alt="Vasiliki" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-2 object-cover border border-white/10 group-hover:border-white/30 transition-colors" />
                        <div class="text-white text-sm font-medium">Vasiliki</div>
                        <div class="text-zinc-500 text-xs">COO</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Links & Legal -->
        <section class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <!-- Social -->
                    <div class="rounded-2xl bg-zinc-900/30 p-6">
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Links</h3>
                        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
                            <a href="https://x.com/ns2agi" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex justify-between text-zinc-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                                <span>X</span>
                                <span>@ns2agi</span>
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/north-star-agi" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex justify-between text-zinc-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                                <span>LinkedIn</span>
                                <span>North Star</span>
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://github.com/North-Star-AGI" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex justify-between text-zinc-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                                <span>GitHub</span>
                                <span>North-Star-AGI</span>
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://discord.gg/m5Hknymurb" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex justify-between text-zinc-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                                <span>Discord</span>
                                <span>Join</span>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Legal -->
                    <div class="rounded-2xl bg-zinc-900/30 p-6">
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Legal</h3>
                        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
                            <div class="flex justify-between text-zinc-400">
                                <span>Name</span>
                                <span class="text-white">North Star VZW</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between text-zinc-400">
                                <span>Type</span>
                                <span class="text-white">Belgian Non-Profit</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between text-zinc-400">
                                <span>Enterprise #</span>
                                <span class="text-white font-mono text-xs">BE1025.122.625</span>
                            </div>
                            <a href="https://www.companyweb.be/en/1025122625/north-star-agi" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex justify-between text-zinc-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                                <span>Registry</span>
                                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1">View <ExternalLink className="w-3 h-3" /></span>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact -->
        <section class="container mx-auto px-6 mt-24">
            <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium text-white mb-8 text-center">
                    Join the team
                </h2>
                <div class="rounded-2xl bg-zinc-900/30 p-12 text-center">
                    <p class="text-zinc-400 text-lg mb-4">Reach out to us at</p>
                    <a href="mailto:filip@ns2agi.com" class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium text-white hover:text-zinc-300 transition-colors">
                        filip@ns2agi.com
                    </a>
                </div>
                <!-- <div class="rounded-2xl bg-zinc-900/30 overflow-hidden">
                    <iframe
                        src="https://beaded-pineapple-898.notion.site/ebd/22fd61b47ae280f7bff5c94e04537806"
                        width="100%"
                        height="700"
                        frameborder="0"
                        allowfullscreen
                        class="w-full"
                        title="Join Form"
                    ></iframe>
                </div> -->
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
